# Flipkart-style UI Project

A frontend-only implementation of Flipkart's Orders, Reviews, and Profile UI.

## Features
- My Orders page with order tracking
- Reviews & Ratings system
- User Profile with editable information
- Responsive design
- No backend required

## How to Run
1. Open `index.html` in any modern browser
2. Navigate between sections using the sidebar or header

## File Structure
- `index.html` - Main dashboard page
- `styles.css` - Global styles
- `script.js` - Main JavaScript logic
- `orders.html` - Detailed orders page
- `orders.css` - Orders page styles
- `orders.js` - Orders page JavaScript

## Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3 (Flexbox, Grid)
- Vanilla JavaScript
- Font Awesome icons
- Google Fonts

## Notes
- All data is stored locally in JavaScript objects
- No data persistence between page reloads
- UI-only functionality (no real backend integration)